	<p>
		<a name=about></a><img SRC="images/about.png" height=16 width=120 />
		<blockquote>
			<p align="justify">
				So, what is UNIX assembly programming?
				Well, one tells you it is a nightmare.
				Or that it is obsolete, because of hardware platform dependence and difficulty.
				Or whatever else..
			</p>
			<p align="justify">
				Here you will find that writing UNIX assembly programs is simple and even has several advantages.
				However it is true that this is not for everyone.
				Mainly this site is for crazy hackers who always do everything in pure assembly :)
				We assume you are familiar with assembly language and with UNIX and have some programming experience;
				our goal is to give you the very secret lore and lift the shroud of mystery over UNIX assembly programming.
			</p>
